modName: Curse of the Lord - SilkroadR Warlock Spell
summary: Curse of the Lord is based off the Warlock Skill Vampire Touch/Kiss from the game SilkroadR.
descriptionHtml:
This is my forth mod for Skyrim. This one is called Curse of the Lord, a powerful spell that drains 50 health and stamina and damages the enemy's magicka as well. It uses the sound effects of the Warlock skill from Silkroad called Vampire Kiss/Death Flower.

Find the Spell Tome at Solitude's Temple of the Divines.
author: Bronyphony
